    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "You can swap any two tiles that are direct neighbours: Double tap to select a tile to swap, then move up, left, right or down and double tap again to swap places with that gem. \nTo cancel the swap, double tap any tile that is not a direct neighbour."
